(25793, 'Regcor 10 mg 10 tab.', 'ريجكور 10مجم 10 اقراص', '16', '16', 'Amlodipine', 'Eipico', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Antihypertensive.selective calcium channel blocker', '10 mg', 'Amlodipine may be used alone or in combination with other antihypertensive and antianginal agents for the treatment of the following conditions [FDA label]:
